<PageTitle>How to use this site</PageTitle>

<MudText Typo="Typo.h3" GutterBottom="true">Starting a new game</MudText>
<MudText>Starting a new game is as easy as filling out the form and hitting the button on the home page.  It will create a new empty game with a unique alphanumeric id.  Make a note of the id and keep it handy for later.  It is how you will invite other people to join your game.</MudText>

<MudText Typo="Typo.h3" GutterBottom="true">Joining a game</MudText>
<MudText>To join a game that someone has invited you to, use the id you were given to first find the game, and then create a username/password combination.  Once you enter that you will be dropped into the main game page.  Returning players can use the sign in section to verify that they are permitted to access the information for a fleet.</MudText>

